This is a Great old classic in which you venture through a dungon to the lower levels, like the original diablo but the enermys will respawn :) which is great because diablo kinda let me down on lack of combat :). With the ability to use magic, be a barbarian or even a rouge with ranged weapons the possibilitys of different combat combinations are endless.

The whole pet system seemed odd at first but once you get use to it you will be feeding your dog or cat fish for days, turning them in to giant monsterous killing machines.

if your a classic rpg fan then this is for you :)
